quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,254,“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Perekani mwa zimene takupatsani lisanadze tsiku lomwe lilibe kugula (chilichonse chokupulumutsani) ngakhale ubwenzi ngakhalenso dandaulo. Ndipo osakhulupirira ndiwo anthu oipa
  2,255,"Allah palibe wopembedzedwa wina koma Iye, Wamoyo wamuyaya, Woimira ndi Woteteza chilichonse. Kusinza sikumgwira ngakhale tulo. Zonse za kumwamba ndi za pansi nza Iye. Kodi ndani angathe kuombola kwa Iye popanda chilolezo chake? Akudziwa za patsogolo ndi zomwe zili pambuyo pawo ndipo zolengedwazo sizidziwa chilichonse pa zomwe zili m’kudziwa Kwake kupatula chimene wafuna. Mpando wake wachifumu wakwanira kumwamba ndi pansi ndipo sizimamvuta kuzisunga zimenezo. Ndipo Iye (Yekha) Njemwe ali Wapamwambamwamba, Ngwamkulu kwabasi, (Ngolemekezeka kwambiri)"
  2,256,"“Palibe kukakamiza (munthu kulowa) m’chipembedzo; kulungama kwaonekera poyera kusiyana ndi kusalungama. Choncho amene akumkana satana nakhulupirira Allah, ndiye kuti wagwira chigwiliro cholimba, chomwe sichisweka. Ndipo Allah Ngwakumva; Ngodziwa"
  2,257,"“Allah ndi Mtetezi wa amene akhulupirira, amawatulutsa kumdima ndikuwalowetsa mkuunika, koma amene sadakhulupirire, atetezi awo ndi asatana. Amawatulutsa m’kuunika ndi kuwalowetsa mu mdima; iwo ndi anthu a ku Moto. M’menemo adzakhalamo nthawi yaitali"